al \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2015/03_preistraeger_2015/03_preistraeger_2015.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223140743/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2015/03_preistraeger_2015/03_preistraeger_2015.html|archivedate=23 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[66th Berlin International Film Festival|2016]] ||data-sort-value=\"Dyrholm\"| [[Trine Dyrholm]] || Anna || data-sort-value=\"Commune\" | ''[[The Commune]]'' || ''Kollektivet'' || {{flagu|Denmark}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=66th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2016/03_preistraeger_2016/03_preistraeger_2016.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223140732/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2016/03_preistraeger_2016/03_preistraeger_2016.html|archivedate=23 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[67th Berlin International Film Festival|2017]] ||data-sort-value=\"Kim\"| [[Kim Min-hee (actress, born 1982)|Kim Min-hee]] || Young-hee || data-sort-value=\"On\" | ''[[On the Beach at Night Alone]]'' || ''\ubc24\uc758 \ud574\ubcc0\uc5d0\uc11c \ud63c\uc790'' || {{flagu|South Korea}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=67th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2017/03_preistraeger_2017/03_preistraeger_2017.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223140644/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2017/03_preistraeger_2017/03_preistraeger_2017.html|archivedate=23 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[68th Berlin International Film Festival|2018]] ||data-sort-value=\"Brun\"| [[Ana Brun]] || Chela || data-sort-value=\"Heiresses\" | 