st]]'' || ''\u0412\u043b\u044e\u0431\u043b\u0451\u043d \u043f\u043e \u0441\u043e\u0431\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u043c\u0443 \u0436\u0435\u043b\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044e'' || {{flagu|Soviet Union}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=33rd Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1983/03_preistraeger_1983/03_Preistraeger_1983.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[34th Berlin International Film Festival|1984]] ||data-sort-value=\"Churikova\"| [[Inna Churikova]] || Vera || data-sort-value=\"Wartime\" | ''[[Wartime Romance]]'' || ''\u0412\u043e\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e-\u043f\u043e\u043b\u0435\u0432\u043e\u0439 \u0440\u043e\u043c\u0430\u043d'' || {{flagu|Soviet Union}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=34th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1984/03_preistraeger_1984/03_Preistraeger_1984.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[35th Berlin International Film Festival|1985]] ||data-sort-value=\"Kennedy\"| [[Jo Kennedy]] || Mary || colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Wrong\" | ''[[Wrong World]]'' || {{flagu|Australia}}  ||<ref>{{cite web|title=35th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1985/03_preistraeger_1985/03_Preistraeger_1985.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2| [[36th Berlin International Film Festival|1986]] ||data-sort-value=\"Valandrey\"| [[Charlotte Valandrey]] (Tie) || Nadia || data-sort-value=\"Red\" | ''[[Red Kiss]]'' || ''Rouge Baiser'' || {{flagu|France}} || rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|title=36th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1986/03_preistraege