 Little House]]'' || ''\u5c0f\u3055\u3044\u304a\u3046\u3061'' || {{flagu|Japan}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=64th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2014/03_preistraeger_2014/preistraeger_2014.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[65th Berlin International Film Festival|2015]] ||data-sort-value=\"Rampling\"| [[Charlotte Rampling]] || Kate Mercer \u2021 || colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"45\" | ''[[45 Years]]'' || {{flagu|United Kingdom}}<br>{{flagu|France}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=65th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2015/03_preistraeger_2015/03_preistraeger_2015.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[66th Berlin International Film Festival|2016]] ||data-sort-value=\"Dyrholm\"| [[Trine Dyrholm]] || Anna || data-sort-value=\"Commune\" | ''[[The Commune]]'' || ''Kollektivet'' || {{flagu|Denmark}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=66th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2016/03_preistraeger_2016/03_preistraeger_2016.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[67th Berlin International Film Festival|2017]] ||data-sort-value=\"Kim\"| [[Kim Min-hee (actress, born 1982)|Kim Min-hee]] || Young-hee || data-sort-value=\"On\" | ''[[On the Beach at Night Alone]]'' || ''\ubc24\uc758 \ud574\ubcc0\uc5d0\uc11c \ud63c\uc790'' || {{flagu|South Korea}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=67th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/2017/03_preistraeger_2017/03_preistraeger_2017.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[68th Berlin Internation